subject: Dear Sir/Ma.
body:
Dear Sir/Ma.
Hope my message meet you in Good health. Your atm card is available
for pick up Please contact DHL on the email address below. and
reconfirm your home address for delivery to your door step.
Also reconfirm your mobile number.
DHL OFFICE EMAIL ADDRESS BELOW
Email: 
ourdhlcourierservices@gmail.com
Regards,
Mrs. Georgieva Kristalina
Head of Transfer/Foreign Payment
Capital One Bank.

subject: Re:   Dear Sir/Ma.
body:
Dear Mrs. Georgieva Kristalina,

Thank you for your message. I am in good health and hope the same for you.

Before I proceed with providing my personal information, could you please provide more details about this ATM card? I don't recall applying or qualifying for one. 

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Brenda
